>>PENG: Well, the sword finger
is more for the healing,

00:36:27.720 --> 00:36:28.636 align:middle line:90%
you're healing others.

00:36:28.636 --> 00:36:29.425 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh, great.

00:36:29.425 --> 00:36:30.120 align:middle line:90%
Let's learn, that'd be great.

00:36:30.120 --> 00:36:31.620 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: Yeah, you're
healing others.

