>>PENG: A handle.

00:36:47.328 --> 00:36:48.020 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Uh huh.

00:36:48.020 --> 00:36:51.833 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: Actually it's like
the handle of the blade--

00:36:51.833 --> 00:36:52.740 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Of the sword.

00:36:52.740 --> 00:36:53.840 align:middle line:90%
>>PENG: --of the sword.

00:36:53.840 --> 00:36:55.020 align:middle line:90%
Then, what is the blade?

00:36:55.020 --> 00:36:57.433 align:middle line:84%
The blade is the
energy shooting out.

00:36:57.433 --> 00:36:57.933 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:36:57.933 --> 00:36:58.680 align:middle line:90%
>>PENG: Yeah.

00:36:58.680 --> 00:37:00.820 align:middle line:84%
Well, when I'm
training people, I

00:37:00.820 --> 00:37:02.455 align:middle line:84%
ask them to use
the body breathing.

00:37:02.455 --> 00:37:02.955 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:37:02.955 --> 00:37:07.042 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: So you inhale, open
all the pores of your skin.

00:37:07.042 --> 00:37:09.710 align:middle line:84%
Now you collect the chi,
and when you exhale,

00:37:09.710 --> 00:37:12.270 align:middle line:84%
you shoot out from
your fingertips.

00:37:12.270 --> 00:37:13.590 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:37:13.590 --> 00:37:15.090 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: Let's try
for half a minute.

00:37:15.090 --> 00:37:15.990 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK, you do it first.

00:37:15.990 --> 00:37:18.230 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: Inhale, open all
the pores of your skin,

00:37:18.230 --> 00:37:21.460 align:middle line:90%
instead of nose-- besides nose.

00:37:21.460 --> 00:37:23.620 align:middle line:84%
Exhale, shoot out from
these two fingertips.

00:37:23.620 --> 00:37:27.080 align:middle line:90%


