Inhale, open all the
pores of the skin.

00:37:31.490 --> 00:37:36.400 align:middle line:84%
Exhale, shoot out
from the fingertips.

00:37:36.400 --> 00:37:38.010 align:middle line:90%
Inhale, open the pores.

00:37:38.010 --> 00:37:40.650 align:middle line:90%


00:37:40.650 --> 00:37:44.230 align:middle line:90%
Exhale, shoot out.

00:37:44.230 --> 00:37:44.940 align:middle line:90%
You can feel it--

00:37:44.940 --> 00:37:45.440 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:37:45.440 --> 00:37:46.100 align:middle line:90%
>>PENG: --the pressure of it.

00:37:46.100 --> 00:37:48.404 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I'm actually getting out
of the way of yours, because--

00:37:48.404 --> 00:37:50.000 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: No, that's
good for healing.

00:37:50.000 --> 00:37:51.416 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's good
for healing, OK.

00:37:51.416 --> 00:37:52.940 align:middle line:90%
>>PENG: Yeah.

00:37:52.940 --> 00:37:57.290 align:middle line:84%
Well, in my book and my DVDs,
I show all different patterns

00:37:57.290 --> 00:37:58.980 align:middle line:90%
you can play.

00:37:58.980 --> 00:38:02.020 align:middle line:84%
You can imagine the
light of energy's

00:38:02.020 --> 00:38:04.440 align:middle line:84%
coming out from your
fingertips, like flashlight.

00:38:04.440 --> 00:38:05.610 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

