through your palm.

00:38:15.130 --> 00:38:15.775 align:middle line:90%
And move away.

00:38:15.775 --> 00:38:16.972 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Uh huh.

00:38:16.972 --> 00:38:18.680 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: Now we begin
to feel that, right?

00:38:18.680 --> 00:38:19.060 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:38:19.060 --> 00:38:19.530 align:middle line:90%
>>PENG: Yeah.

00:38:19.530 --> 00:38:20.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:38:20.030 --> 00:38:22.210 align:middle line:84%
>>PENG: Cutting
through, move away.

00:38:22.210 --> 00:38:26.810 align:middle line:84%
Or, you can like, dip--
like dip under water.

00:38:26.810 --> 00:38:28.330 align:middle line:90%
You feel the pulse on your palm?

00:38:28.330 --> 00:38:28.830 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:38:28.830 --> 00:38:29.100 align:middle line:90%
>>PENG: Good

